##DISPLAYNAME Shutdown All
##DESCRIPTION Shuts down all XVMs in the system

assume launch-all has run

// stop the send driver
stop the perfdriver-send-driver app in the perfdriver-send-driver xvm

// shutdown the processor cluster
stop the perfdriver app in the perfdriver-2 xvm
stop the perfdriver app in the perfdriver-1 xvm

// stop the receive driver
stop the perfdriver-receive-driver app in the perfdriver-receive-driver xvm

shutdown
